
Description
===========

Create a file with 2 single particles ("particle gun")
The distribution of particles is flat in energy up to  E(max), in GeV. 
Particles are uniformly distributed in phi and angle
S.Chekanov (ANL)

Setup:
======
source setup.sh
javac promc_gun.java 

Usage: java promc_gun pions.promc 100 211 1000

This means:

E=100        # max energy 100 GeV
ID=211       # pi+ or use and PDG ID
EVENTS=1000  # Nr of generated events with 1 particle

